                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Implement a queue using two stacks. The queue should support peek, pop, push, and empty operations. Push elements into an input stack; move all elements to an output stack lazily when dequeuing. Each element is moved at most once, giving amortized O(1) per operation."
